94
0:04:54,000 --> 0:04:56,000
but it's some other dog." Right?

95
0:04:56,000 --> 0:04:58,000
Now, you try using the Freudian explanation there.

96
0:04:58,000 --> 0:04:59,000
(Laughter)

97
0:04:59,000 --> 0:05:03,000
